Class ValenceSpreader.Result<TermType,DocIdType>

    public static class ValenceSpreader.Result<TermType,DocIdType>
extends java.lang.Object
    The return type from running the spreadValence methods. This reports the weights assigned to all of the input documents and all of the terms that existed in all of the documents.
